queries.sql: select p.*, concat(a.clave, " ", a.nombre) as asignatura, concat(u.nombre, " ", u.apaterno, " ", u.amaterno) as docente, c.nombre as carrera from programacion as p right join asignaturas as a on p.materia_id = a.id left join usuarios as u on p.docente_id = u.id left join carreras as c on p.carrera_id = c.id
